<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>International&#174; T 444E Diesel Engine - Model Years Late 1997 to 2003 - Oil Cooler And Filter - Oil
        Cooler - Inspection
    </stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcproc graphiccount="0">
        <title>Inspection</title>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Inspect oil cooler for blocked tubes and corrosion where the tubes are assembled to the oil
                cooler bundle. Replace the oil cooler bundle if required.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Inspect filter header for blocked orifices and damaged threads at the oil filter threaded
                inserts.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove any debris that may be blocking the oil flow passages.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">If thread damage is apparent, replace the header.</para>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
